--[[
    ╔══════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ║         SECRET CHAT LOCALSCRIPT          ║
    ║  Only visible between players with this  ║
    ║  exact script. Handshake-verified chat.  ║
    ╚══════════════════════════════════════════╝

    HOW IT WORKS:
    • On load, your client broadcasts a silent handshake tag via chat.
    • Any other player running this script detects the tag and marks
      you as a "verified" user — and vice versa.
    • Secret messages are prefixed with a hidden tag. Players WITHOUT
      the script see nothing. Players WITH it see the custom chat GUI.
    • A periodic ping re-verifies users every ~10 seconds.

    CONTROLS:
    • Press [Right Shift] to toggle the chat window.
    • Press [Enter] inside the text box to send a message.
    • Drag the title bar to move the window.

    NOTE: Roblox's SafeChat filter may sanitize outgoing messages in
    some servers/accounts. This script works best on 13+ accounts or
    in games with relaxed chat filtering. If handshakes are filtered,
    mutual detection may not occur.
]]

